Document: CameraTexture
Path: godot/classes/class_cameratexture.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the CameraTexture class

Properties:
- int: camera_feed_id. Default: 0
- bool: camera_is_active. Default: false
- bool: resource_local_to_scene. Default: false (overrides Resource's resource_local_to_scene)
- FeedImage (enum_CameraServer_FeedImage): which_feed. Default: 0

Note: resource_local_to_scene overrides the Resource class's resource_local_to_scene property.
