Document: CameraTexture
Path: godot/classes/class_cameratexture.rst
Summary: Properties and accessors for managing camera feed settings and image selection in CameraTexture.

camera_feed_id (int): The ID of the CameraFeed for which we want to display the image. Default: 0. Set via set_camera_feed_id(value: int), get via get_camera_feed_id().

camera_is_active (bool): Convenience property that gives access to the active property of the CameraFeed. Default: false. Set via set_camera_active(value: bool), get via get_camera_active().

which_feed (FeedImage (enum)): Which image within the CameraFeed we want access to, important if the camera image is split in a Y and CbCr component. Default: 0. Set via set_which_feed(value: FeedImage), get via get_which_feed().